highlights.text: Taylor Swift has the most spots on Top Songs USA. “Cruel Summer” is the highest at #11.
“Loser, Baby” by Keith David, Blake Roman, Andrew Underberg, and Sam Haft is the biggest gainer on Top Songs USA, up 79 spots at #71.
“BANDIT” by Don Toliver is the highest new entry on Top Songs USA at #15.
“No Role Modelz” by J. Cole has been on Top Songs USA the longest, at 194 weeks straight.
